<div class="card musician-tip-card">
  <h2>Will Freed</h2>

	<img src="/images/musicians/will_freed.jpg" alt="Will Freed" />

	<h3>About Will</h3>
	<p>
		Will Freed is a singer/songwriter who grew up in West Virginia, but now calls Columbus home. Will began playing for a living at an early age – developing his own style, writing music and learning how to play 100s of covers in his own unique, heartwarming tone. He lives in Grove City with his wife Ashley.
	</p>

	<h3>Will's Social</h3>
	<ul>
		<li><a href="https://twitter.com/willfreed">Twitter</a></li>
		<li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/willfreedband/">Instagram</a></li>
		<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/thewillfreedband/">Facebook</a></li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Tip Will</h3>
	<a role="button" class="button" href="https://cash.app/$willfreed1">CashApp</a>
	<a role="button" class="button" href="https://venmo.com/will-freed-1">Venmo</a>
	<a role="button" class="button" href="https://www.paypal.me/willfreed">PayPal</a>

</div>

<div class="card musician-tip-card">
  <h2>KaTanya Ingram</h2>

	<img src="/images/musicians/katanya_ingram.jpg" alt="Katanya Ingram" />

	<h3>About KaTanya</h3>
	<p>
		KaTanya believes that music brings people together. She grew up in a military family and has traveled the world from Italy to the United States, Germany and back again. Although not originally from Columbus, she’s inspired by the vast opportunities to enjoy many types of artistic expression in Columbus and its surrounding areas. She identifies not as a singer or vocalist but as a street performer, and enjoys putting smiles on faces and creating a joyful atmosphere in public spaces.
	</p>

	<h3>KaTanya's Social</h3>
