	<img src="/images/musicians/jordidge.jpg" alt="Jordidge" />

	<h3>About Jordidge</h3>
	<p>
		Jordidge’s work is derived from his love for words, emotion and philosophies. With every piece, he wants people to dig down and get “the feels”. The kind that linger long after you have forgotten what you experienced. He plays the acoustic/electric guitar with soulful vocals, mostly original songs with the occasional cover.
	</p>

